  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For motorcycle enthusiasts looking to spend enjoyable time at their computer, Motorcycle Night Ride offers a wonderful option with its soothing atmosphere.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those who want to escape the hectic pace, focus on scenic views, and simply enjoy the ride, this game delivers exactly that kind of experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A dynamic atmosphere enriched with sunsets, nighttime rides, and various weather conditions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- No race stress, no chasing after objectives—just scenery, the sound of the motorbike, and a relaxing vibe.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Simple and smooth driving mechanics instead of complex controls.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The freedom to ride without the stress of traffic or the pressure of competition.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game focuses on peace and relaxation rather than speed and adrenaline.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s perfect for unwinding after a long day and enjoying a pleasant experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/abfcad4c39844a18be70a3496231e419.avif?t=1764265480\" width=608 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy night driving with different engines. Each engine offers a unique experience with its unique sound and driving feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/fa4a05f6ebb029153638d85cca283376.poster.avif?t=1764265480\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/fa4a05f6ebb029153638d85cca283376.webm?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/48c53c2d623ef45418380e97c0f39894.avif?t=1764265480\" width=608 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Drive on more than 10 maps enriched with majestic city lights, quiet countryside, coastal roads and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/710709ccc369f79467ca6eee6fffc8b0.webp?t=1764265480\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/710709ccc369f79467ca6eee6fffc8b0.poster.avif?t=1764265480\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=420 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/9c81ac684c4923bca0f5e7466967c944.avif?t=1764265480\" width=608 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Enjoy the roads endlessly, without the stress of missions or racing. Just the scenery, the sound of the engine and a peaceful driving experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/01fd66e8b1f4ff4bbe76d56a03fbb437.poster.avif?t=1764265480\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/01fd66e8b1f4ff4bbe76d56a03fbb437.webm?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/01fd66e8b1f4ff4bbe76d56a03fbb437.mp4?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/fbc8189e6e2fb6ac22e06521e522de2a.avif?t=1764265480\" width=608 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a detailed and realistic crash system, react differently every time you crash. Recover your bike and continue your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/c149bed689c660bd06436f3a743dd5af.poster.avif?t=1764265480\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/c149bed689c660bd06436f3a743dd5af.webm?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/c149bed689c660bd06436f3a743dd5af.mp4?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Those tired of competitive games,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Players seeking a tranquil gaming experience,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Anyone who wants to feel the wind through the sound of a motorbike—this game is truly calming.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your helmet, gently twist the throttle, and savor the freedom—even if it’s just on screen!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For motorcycle enthusiasts looking to spend enjoyable time at their computer, Motorcycle Night Ride offers a wonderful option with its soothing atmosphere.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those who want to escape the hectic pace, focus on scenic views, and simply enjoy the ride, this game delivers exactly that kind of experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A dynamic atmosphere enriched with sunsets, nighttime rides, and various weather conditions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- No race stress, no chasing after objectives—just scenery, the sound of the motorbike, and a relaxing vibe.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Simple and smooth driving mechanics instead of complex controls.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The freedom to ride without the stress of traffic or the pressure of competition.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game focuses on peace and relaxation rather than speed and adrenaline.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s perfect for unwinding after a long day and enjoying a pleasant experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/abfcad4c39844a18be70a3496231e419.avif?t=1764265480\" width=608 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy night driving with different engines. Each engine offers a unique experience with its unique sound and driving feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/fa4a05f6ebb029153638d85cca283376.poster.avif?t=1764265480\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/fa4a05f6ebb029153638d85cca283376.webm?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/webm;