"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/fbc8189e6e2fb6ac22e06521e522de2a.avif?t=1764265480\" width=608 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a detailed and realistic crash system, react differently every time you crash. Recover your bike and continue your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/c149bed689c660bd06436f3a743dd5af.poster.avif?t=1764265480\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/c149bed689c660bd06436f3a743dd5af.webm?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/c149bed689c660bd06436f3a743dd5af.mp4?t=1764265480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Those tired of competitive games,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Players seeking a tranquil gaming experience,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Anyone who wants to feel the wind through the sound of a motorbike—this game is truly calming.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your helmet, gently twist the throttle, and savor the freedom—even if it’s just on screen!</p>",
